==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: jūnzĭ bàochóu, shí nián bù wăn
===Etymology===
Literally: (For) a gentleman to take revenge, ten years is not too late (to wait).
===Proverb===
'''[[君子]][[報仇]]，[[十]][[年]][[不]][[晚]]'''
# One should bide one's time and wait for the right opportunity to seek vengeance.
===Alternative forms===
[[君子报仇，十年不晚]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
